sathyameva jayathe is a 2001 indian malayalam action thriller film , directed by viji thampi .   the film stars suresh gopi , aishwarya , balachandramenon , mini nair and siddique in lead roles .   this film became a super hit and the turning point of siddique 's career as the top villain in malayalam films .   the film had musical score by c. rajamani and songs by m. jayachandran .